description: Etrion Corp. engages in the production of renewable energy. The company is headquartered in Geneve, Geneve and currently employs 17 full-time employees.  The firm develops, builds, owns and operates ground-based solar photovoltaic (PV) power generation plants in Japan also is contributing to the diversification of the energy mix by leveraging the abundance of renewable resources to generate solar energy.
